name: Project Galaxy Space Expedition - Star Map
description:
Participate campaigns on Galaxy to get entries to collect the 3 missing NFTs - - "Star Map”, “Eternal Compass” “Starship”. Forge your final spaceship [Space Expedition - Pisces](https://galaxy.eco/galaxy/campaign/GCDtiUUxFw)! 

Only participation in campaigns that met the following criteria within the campaign perid is counted towards the credentials
1. The campaign must be initiated by a verified space
2. The campaign must be a public campaign
3. The campaign must NOT be an open-to-all campaigns

Users can read more about our campaign[ here ](https://medium.com/@projectgalaxy/project-galaxy-introduces-the-space-expedition-campaign-eb17543ff3f)
